00:00:40.920 --> 00:00:43.920
explanation,

00:00:44.160 --> 00:00:49.000
some sort of all embracing

00:00:49.240 --> 00:00:52.200
idea, concept, vision,

00:00:52.400 --> 00:00:57.480
which places creation into a context,

00:00:58.320 --> 00:01:00.320
somewhere there.

00:01:00.520 --> 00:01:04.240
That seeking has taken us in many directions.

00:01:04.440 --> 00:01:07.160
Some of us to

00:01:07.360 --> 00:01:11.160
false and damaging teachers,

00:01:11.360 --> 00:01:14.960
some to drugs,

00:01:15.200 --> 00:01:20.200
some to opting out,

00:01:21.400 --> 00:01:23.720
but

00:01:23.920 --> 00:01:26.480
so, it’s led everybody else of course everybody here tonight

00:01:26.680 --> 00:01:30.480
to this particular function.

00:01:34.280 --> 00:01:40.240
Shri Mataji is offering an experience.

00:01:41.880 --> 00:01:47.080
It's not self-certification, it's not like being

00:01:47.280 --> 00:01:50.160
born again, I am born again, I am born again.

00:01:50.360 --> 00:01:52.120
It's not a statement of belief,

00:01:52.320 --> 00:01:56.600
it is an actual physical happening.

00:01:56.880 --> 00:02:01.400
And that physical happening is known as Self-realization.

00:02:01.640 --> 00:02:04.360
It's known as the Ruh to the Muslims,

00:02:04.560 --> 00:02:10.200
it's known as the Moksha to the Hindus,

00:02:10.400 --> 00:02:13.480
is known as enlightenment, liberation,

00:02:13.680 --> 00:02:15.800
second birth.

00:02:16.080 --> 00:02:17.600
There are a number of names for it.

00:02:17.800 --> 00:02:22.360
Christ referred to it as the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost.

00:02:22.760 --> 00:02:25.880
But it is all the same thing, it is

00:02:26.120 --> 00:02:31.760
this experience which links the energy within us

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:35.320
to the all pervading energy of God.

00:02:35.520 --> 00:02:39.120
The yoga, yoga means union,

00:02:39.320 --> 00:02:42.200
and that union is in fact this,

00:02:42.480 --> 00:02:44.920
the union of this energy here

00:02:45.200 --> 00:02:48.600
which lies in the sacrum bone at the bottom of the spine,

00:02:48.800 --> 00:02:52.720
is a physical thing, which in the presence of an authorised person

00:02:52.920 --> 00:02:55.280
rises through the central channel

00:02:55.480 --> 00:03:00.400
and piercing the top of the head, the fontanel bone,

00:03:00.600 --> 00:03:03.240
actually comes from the top of the head as a cool breeze.

00:03:03.440 --> 00:03:11.320
It also manifests on the hands as cool vibrations.

00:03:11.680 --> 00:03:13.920
And another thing that happens then is,

00:03:14.160 --> 00:03:15.880
that this, these cool vibrations

00:03:16.120 --> 00:03:19.680
and this experience, makes one collectively conscious.

00:03:19.920 --> 00:03:24.280
It is a new step, it is another step in evolution.

00:03:24.480 --> 00:03:29.440
It is, perhaps to put it one way, a move from

00:03:29.640 --> 00:03:34.200
the human being to a spiritual being.

00:03:35.760 --> 00:03:38.920
Now what happens when this,

00:03:39.360 --> 00:03:44.080
the Kundalini, this energy at the bottom of the spine rises?

00:03:44.400 --> 00:03:48.640
It pierces a number of energy centers in the body.

