00:04:27.840 --> 00:04:29.400
The desire for creation came,

00:04:29.600 --> 00:04:32.600
which is represented here by this left channel.

00:04:32.840 --> 00:04:37.200
Then, what we with the Christian background know

00:04:37.400 --> 00:04:40.120
as the Holy Ghost or Holy Spirit,

00:04:40.320 --> 00:04:43.920
then became the force, that force of God

00:04:44.200 --> 00:04:47.120
which brought about creation.

00:04:47.400 --> 00:04:50.720
And creation is two parts, or two parts of it,

00:04:50.920 --> 00:04:54.640
two aspects of it I should say. One is the desire

00:04:54.840 --> 00:04:57.720
and the other is the creation itself.

00:04:57.920 --> 00:05:00.320
So we have two

00:05:00.920 --> 00:05:04.400
channels, on the left and the right.

00:05:04.600 --> 00:05:07.240
One on the left and one on the right.

00:05:07.480 --> 00:05:11.040
The left hand one is concerned with

00:05:11.240 --> 00:05:15.240
yesterday, the past, the female aspect in us,

00:05:15.720 --> 00:05:19.840
the emotional,

00:05:20.560 --> 00:05:25.560
that sense of desire, introspection.

00:05:25.760 --> 00:05:30.040
The right hand side is action.

00:05:30.240 --> 00:05:33.560
That is tomorrow, that is

00:05:34.200 --> 00:05:36.640
planning, that is organising, that is dominating,

00:05:36.840 --> 00:05:39.000
that is being an outgoing personality,

00:05:39.200 --> 00:05:42.440
that is putting the attention out all the time.

00:05:42.640 --> 00:05:45.480
Taken to an extreme in the left

00:05:45.680 --> 00:05:50.400
there is a tendency or extending the left rather,

00:05:50.600 --> 00:05:53.160
one comes into the subconscious.

00:05:53.360 --> 00:05:57.760
Everything that has happened in the past is here.

00:05:58.000 --> 00:06:02.120
It is possible further one comes to the left

00:06:02.320 --> 00:06:06.960
the more one comes involved in the past.

00:06:07.200 --> 00:06:09.680
And it is possible on the right hand side

00:06:09.880 --> 00:06:12.800
for this to go further and further into the right,

00:06:13.000 --> 00:06:18.920
and so it becomes fanatical, dry

00:06:20.640 --> 00:06:25.240
and that's the area of heart attacks and

00:06:25.440 --> 00:06:30.600
those overactive diseases which are so prevalent in the West.

00:06:30.800 --> 00:06:33.800
The West tends to be very active.

00:06:34.000 --> 00:06:38.080
The Eastern countries tend to be more on the left.

00:06:38.320 --> 00:06:40.800
Well, we talk about left and right, what does that mean?

00:06:41.080 --> 00:06:43.560
I was pointing out the other night that if we say something,

00:06:43.760 --> 00:06:47.120
"Oh I wish I hadn't said that to somebody,” now that's on the left,

00:06:47.360 --> 00:06:49.880
"Oh I wish I hadn't said that.

00:06:50.160 --> 00:06:52.920
Tomorrow when I see him again I will say this to him,”

00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:55.200
that's on the right.

00:06:55.400 --> 00:06:58.520
So we have gone, "Oh gee I am sorry",

00:06:58.720 --> 00:07:01.440
and we have come over to the right for tomorrow I will do this.

00:07:01.640 --> 00:07:04.280
At the point of crossing there is this little moment

00:07:04.520 --> 00:07:08.040
right in the center and that is 'now',

00:07:08.280 --> 00:07:10.080
when crossed from the past

00:07:10.320 --> 00:07:12.200
from the past to the future,

00:07:12.400 --> 00:07:15.360
there is a crossing point which is 'now'.

00:07:15.560 --> 00:07:18.760
And that crossing point is this central channel

00:07:19.040 --> 00:07:21.160
that the Kundalini, this energy,

00:07:21.360 --> 00:07:25.320
rises up in the process of Self-realization.

00:07:25.520 --> 00:07:30.640
Rising - this Mooladhara sits actually below,

00:07:30.840 --> 00:07:34.440
the energy center sits below the source of the Kundalini,

00:07:34.640 --> 00:07:38.880
where the Kundalini originates in the sacrum bone.

