Nabhi is concerned with our sustenance. In other words

00:07:52.080 --> 00:07:55.160
we are not, if you like to think of it in terms of evolution

00:07:55.360 --> 00:07:57.760
the Mooladhara is concerned with that innocence

00:07:57.960 --> 00:07:59.880
that original innocence.

00:08:00.080 --> 00:08:01.600
Then comes the consciousness,

00:08:01.800 --> 00:08:04.880
the need for food, for shelter, those basic needs,

00:08:05.080 --> 00:08:07.480
that is the territory of the Nabhi.

00:08:07.720 --> 00:08:11.120
