people begin to wonder which way to turn,

00:13:03.200 --> 00:13:07.440
who is truth and who is falsehood,

00:13:07.680 --> 00:13:11.880
who is the real teacher,

00:13:12.080 --> 00:13:14.240
who is the false teacher.

00:13:14.440 --> 00:13:17.280
Shri Mataji has come to do one job only,

00:13:17.480 --> 00:13:20.720
and that is to awaken this subtle energy within us,

00:13:20.920 --> 00:13:22.640
that energy which we can as

00:13:22.840 --> 00:13:26.480
the reflection of the Holy Ghost within us.

00:13:26.680 --> 00:13:28.640
She’s come to awaken it and put us

00:13:28.840 --> 00:13:31.880
in touch with our Self, our Spirit.

00:13:32.080 --> 00:13:33.600
When that happens

00:13:33.800 --> 00:13:35.920
you begin

00:13:36.200 --> 00:13:38.520
to feel the bliss and the joy

00:13:38.720 --> 00:13:43.200
of that final aspect of your spiritual ascent.

