There are so many anti-Christs,

00:14:05.880 --> 00:14:10.400
there is so many forces of negativity, there is so much confusion

00:14:10.600 --> 00:14:15.120
in the world today and so many

00:14:15.320 --> 00:14:18.720
people have come on this earth whether as

00:14:18.920 --> 00:14:21.040
I said anti-Christs

00:14:21.240 --> 00:14:27.040
or else confused people to mislead us,

00:14:27.240 --> 00:14:30.080
and to perhaps take us through the highways and byways

00:14:30.280 --> 00:14:32.520
in our seeking.

00:14:32.720 --> 00:14:34.720
Self-realization establishes something

00:14:34.920 --> 00:14:37.360
within you in which you can discriminate.

00:14:37.560 --> 00:14:40.600
In which you can know truth from falsehood.

00:14:40.800 --> 00:14:45.240
In Sahaja Yoga which is what happens

00:14:45.440 --> 00:14:47.080
when you get your realization -

00:14:47.280 --> 00:14:52.200
Sahaja Yoga means spontaneous Self-realization -

00:14:52.400 --> 00:14:54.480
when that happens

00:14:54.680 --> 00:14:57.040
you become a collective being.

00:14:57.240 --> 00:14:59.280
You become collectively conscious,

00:14:59.480 --> 00:15:02.200
you start to feel on your finger tips

00:15:02.400 --> 00:15:06.520
the centers of others, you start to feel in your awareness

00:15:06.760 --> 00:15:09.720
what is happening within your own subtle body.

00:15:09.920 --> 00:15:12.240
You can give realization to others.

00:15:12.440 --> 00:15:15.760
You can discriminate between the people who are seekers

00:15:15.960 --> 00:15:20.880
and the people who are false.

00:15:21.080 --> 00:15:24.040
You can discriminate between those who

00:15:24.320 --> 00:15:26.680
wish their spiritual ascent

00:15:26.880 --> 00:15:29.960
and those who are opposing evolution.

00:15:30.160 --> 00:15:34.600
And this is important because we have never had any yard stick

00:15:34.800 --> 00:15:39.280
by which we could judge other than our mental activity,

00:15:39.480 --> 00:15:42.080
other than our emotional activity.

00:15:42.280 --> 00:15:47.760
Now, when you get your Self-realization you have that yard stick.

00:15:47.960 --> 00:15:51.360
You have that immutable measure by which

00:15:51.560 --> 00:15:54.680
you can assume truth.

00:15:54.880 --> 00:15:57.320
When you begin to feel the truth

00:15:57.520 --> 00:15:59.400
on your finger tips

00:15:59.600 --> 00:16:01.360
as the cool wind of the Holy Spirit,

00:16:01.560 --> 00:16:03.760
as that power that lies within you,

00:16:03.960 --> 00:16:07.720
you know for certain that you have met

00:16:07.920 --> 00:16:13.120
that aspect of your nature which is indeed truth.

00:16:13.320 --> 00:16:17.800
There will always be people who try to persuade you otherwise,

00:16:18.000 --> 00:16:21.600
there will always be the prophets of doom

00:16:21.800 --> 00:16:25.680
that this world is going to be destroyed and so many things.

00:16:25.880 --> 00:16:29.840
But just ask yourself if the God Almighty that

00:16:30.040 --> 00:16:35.400
created this earth, is going to destroy His own creation.

00:16:35.600 --> 00:16:38.760
We all have to get our Self-realization.

00:16:38.960 --> 00:16:44.160
We all have to become part and parcel of the Kingdom of God.

00:16:44.360 --> 00:16:48.960
We all have to become witness to the play of the Divine.

00:16:49.160 --> 00:16:52.360
We all have to become like Christ.

00:16:52.560 --> 00:16:56.880
We have to become the principle that is the Spirit.

00:16:57.080 --> 00:16:59.720
And ultimately when we achieve that

00:16:59.920 --> 00:17:02.720
the final joy of Self-realization,

00:17:02.920 --> 00:17:04.920
begins it’s process

00:17:05.120 --> 00:17:09.960
of taking us to that final union with God.

00:17:10.160 --> 00:17:11.680
In Sahaja Yoga

00:17:11.880 --> 00:17:14.800
the first experience of Self-realization may be very subtle,

00:17:15.040 --> 00:17:19.560
it may be very slight, and you may be a little unconvinced.

00:17:19.760 --> 00:17:23.720
Unconvinced rationally or in terms of perception.

00:17:23.920 --> 00:17:26.840
Because as I said this subtle

00:17:27.040 --> 00:17:29.120
cool wind that you begin to feel on your hand

00:17:29.320 --> 00:17:33.120
may in fact be very very slight.

00:17:33.320 --> 00:17:37.200
It may be because this chakra here is a little blocked because

00:17:37.400 --> 00:17:38.920
of damage to that center,

00:17:39.120 --> 00:17:42.440
so don't despair if you don't feel it the first time.

00:17:42.640 --> 00:17:45.120
Know that inside yourself

00:17:45.320 --> 00:17:47.920
something great has happened.

00:17:48.120 --> 00:17:50.360
And when that great happening takes place

00:17:50.560 --> 00:17:53.160
you owe it to yourself to develop it.

00:17:53.360 --> 00:17:56.760
Thousands of people are developing it around the world.

00:17:56.960 --> 00:18:00.960
In Australia it's growing

00:18:01.200 --> 00:18:02.800
and it's growing very strongly.

