00:37:49.640 --> 00:37:53.640
the Ruh, the All Pervading Power, the Chaitanya, the Omkara,

00:37:53.840 --> 00:37:57.600
He came on this earth and He did that job for us,

00:37:57.800 --> 00:38:00.560
because He resides there.

