Now what He said by

00:38:04.200 --> 00:38:08.560
the second birth or by baptism was

00:38:08.760 --> 00:38:10.800
that this Kundalini which is lying

00:38:11.000 --> 00:38:14.200
at the triangular bone there, has to rise.

00:38:14.400 --> 00:38:18.640
Rise and penetrate through this center,

00:38:18.840 --> 00:38:22.600
awaken Jesus Christ there.

00:38:22.800 --> 00:38:25.200
Now the - what great miraculous thing

00:38:25.400 --> 00:38:29.160
He has done that once you awaken this center within us,

00:38:29.360 --> 00:38:32.800
these two institutions on the left and the right,

00:38:33.000 --> 00:38:36.080
one is the ego, another is the super ego;

00:38:36.280 --> 00:38:38.640
one is the ego which gives us

00:38:38.840 --> 00:38:43.320
all ideas about ourselves which are not really self esteem

00:38:43.520 --> 00:38:45.120
but something false.

