And super ego is the

00:38:47.480 --> 00:38:52.400
condition in which we human beings become conditioned,

00:38:52.600 --> 00:38:57.720
in which we accept conditions: I am this, I am this, I am this.

00:38:57.920 --> 00:39:01.360
Both the things are sucked in by the awakening

00:39:01.560 --> 00:39:05.960
of the Kundalini of this great incarnation on this earth.

