Is described, were the three great people

00:40:21.440 --> 00:40:23.680
who went to see Jesus He was born was

00:40:23.880 --> 00:40:29.680
Shri Krishna as Vishnu

00:40:29.880 --> 00:40:32.520
and Mahesha is Shiva,

00:40:32.720 --> 00:40:34.920
and Brahma as Brahmadeva.

