On the contrary blind faith is against Sahaja Yoga.

00:40:59.720 --> 00:41:01.360
It should happen to you first,

00:41:01.560 --> 00:41:04.600
once it happens then you will be amazed

00:41:04.840 --> 00:41:09.320
that you yourself is a very great

00:41:09.520 --> 00:41:12.680
miraculous instrument of God.

00:41:12.880 --> 00:41:15.360
You will be amazed, how this instrument works.

00:41:15.560 --> 00:41:17.160
Even the people who come to Me, say,

00:41:17.360 --> 00:41:19.920
“Mother we are gone cases we are good for nothing,

00:41:20.120 --> 00:41:22.800
we led a very bad life we are inauspicious.”

