not Me. So why there should be a question

00:46:15.760 --> 00:46:17.360
when I am not selling anything,

00:46:17.560 --> 00:46:20.120
when I am not acquiring anything out of you,

00:46:20.320 --> 00:46:23.960
when there is no possibility of you being exploited

00:46:24.200 --> 00:46:26.400
